parts.description:
Provided book is organised as student handout learning materials of Basic English
Grammar. Competency of this level is that students are able to use the following
sentence structure patterns containing grammatical forms covered in this term such
as English Verbs, Nouns, Adjectives, Adverbs, Pronouns, Prepositions, Articles,
Conjunctions, Interjections, and Verbals.
A quiz for testing your basic grammar skills
